CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A3 reads: " 'New Era' Dawns at Herron Hill Junior High - Enjoying Books - Aided by Mrs. Lillian Warner, library clerk, and Ruloff Rulofson, team teacher, students enjoy their library hour."
TitMainTitle: Lillian warner and Ruloff Rulofson, standing among young men and women seated around tables in Herron Hill Junior High School library
